title: Club to rank
body:
Hi, I've asked this before and I got invited to a few clubs but they mostly chat and seldom ask to duo queue. Is there a club/discord for people who look for a duoQ often? Would be really nice to have one. If you know one please share.

(If relevant I'm a Support main at P4 at the moment)

Cheers!

replies.body: At last! Would you like to duo together?! I'm playing regularly and it would be great to play with a sup main (I'm an ADC main) :)
